name: DarkCrypto Foundation
description: DarkCrypto Foundation, previously DarkCrypto Finance, is a brand house of many independent multichain dApps of Defi and Play-to-Earn. Our mission is to make it easily for every user to enjoy when investing in every project. As we move towards more decentralized protocols, we give users the power to decide how each project grows and is funded through a voting system using the governance token $DCF
